                    </form>
                    <p><a href="#" data-reveal-id="overlay_terms_and_conditions">Terms and Conditions</a> apply</p>
                    <div id="overlay_terms_and_conditions" class="reveal-modal" data-reveal>
                        <div class="row padding">
                            <div class="small-12 small-centered medium-10 columns">
                                <h2>Terms and Conditions</h2>
                                <a class="close-reveal-modal">&#215;</a>
                                <p><b>What you need to do in order to qualify for Guaranteed Savings</b></p>
                                <ul>
                                  <li>If you’re a new customer signing up to Powershop:</li>
                                </ul>
                                <p>Send us your most recent bill from your old retailer for your main home (Competitor’s Bill) and we’ll guarantee that you’ll save with Powershop over your first year. We’ll include any rebates or grants of free power we make to you as part of your Guaranteed Savings, such as any account credits you received when you signed up to Powershop. The Competitor’s Bill supplied must be from 1 May 2016 or later and, if we ask, you must supply an original copy of that Competitor’s Bill. Your Guaranteed Savings period will be for 12 months, commencing on the date your switch to Powershop is completed (Guaranteed Savings Period).</p>
                                <ul>
                                  <li>If you’re an existing Powershop customer; or</li>
                                  <li>You’ve just moved into a new home, (either as a new or existing Powershop customer):</li>
                                </ul>

                                <p>You must provide Powershop with written evidence of a competitor’s publicly available electricity price that you have either found or been offered (Competitor’s Offer). The Competitor’s Offer must be currently available at the time you send it to us. Both you and your main home must be eligible for that particular Competitor’s Offer (in other words, you must have the correct metering configuration and fit all other criteria). We may ask for proof of this eligibility in order for us to apply your Guaranteed Savings. Your Guaranteed Savings period will be for 12 months, commencing on the date we receive and accept the Competitor’s Offer from you (Guaranteed Savings Period).</p>
                                <p>Your savings guarantee is based on the actual cost of your electricity with Powershop over the next year for your main home, when compared to the cost of the same amount of electricity using the rates in the Competitor’s Bill or Offer you have provided to us.</p>
                                <p>Powershop can only offer the savings guarantee against Competitors with published rates. We will not guarantee savings on Competitors' Bills or Offers where the rates in those Bills or Offers are based on real time spot market pricing.</p>
                                <p>The savings guarantee only applies to the rates offered by our competitors and does not apply to any additional incentives (like cash offers), or sign up deals. If the Competitor’s Offer is for a fixed period of less than 12 months or only available until a fixed date then your savings guarantee will be valid for that particular period. After that fixed period Powershop will match the best publicly available offer from that same competitor for the remainder of your 12 month Guaranteed Savings period. If the Competitor’s Offer is for a fixed period of longer than 12 months, we will only guarantee that price for the 12 months from the date when we notify you that we’ve accepted the competitor’s price.</p>
                                <p>Certain Powershop products are priced at a premium (e.g. Airshed where the additional amount is used to purchase carbon credits). The additional cost of these products (above your Standard Power rate) is excluded from the Guaranteed Savings calculations. This means that when we calculate your spend for the purposes of the Guaranteed Savings, we will use your Standard Power rate for any premium products you purchase during the period of the savings guarantee.</p>
                                <p>The savings guarantee does not apply if, within your Guaranteed Savings Period: (A) you switch away from Powershop; (B) we reasonably believe after viewing the Competitor’s Bill or Offer, or after you refuse to supply us with the original copy of the Competitor’s Bill, that the rates in the Competitor’s Bill or Offer are not genuine; (C) we reasonably believe the property in question is not your main home; (E) at the time we calculate your Guaranteed Savings you owe Powershop more than $100 which is at least 60 days overdue (whether on this property or another property).</p>
                                <p>If your metering configuration changes through the year (whether due to a change you request, an error we discover, or for any other reason) then we will use our best endeavours to replicate the cost you would have paid for your power under your old Competitor’s Bill, or Competitor’s Offer by using a usage-based weighted average of your old retailer’s rates, or those provided in the Competitor’s Offer and applying this to your new metering configuration. This offer for Guaranteed Savings is per residential account and is not available in conjunction with any other promotional offers available through Powershop from time to time.</p>
                                <p>Powershop at its sole discretion may amend or cease to offer Guaranteed Savings at any time without notice. In such event, any Guaranteed Savings Periods, which commenced prior to the date Powershop ceased to offer them, will continue to be honoured.</p>
                           </div>
                          </div>
