                  <h3>Will my rates change?</h3>
                  <p>Guaranteed Savings won’t change your Powershop rates – it’s more like a safety net for you and the price you pay for power. Buying your monthly Simple Saver and our regular discounted specials is still the best way to save with Powershop.</p>
                  <h3>How do I know I’m saving?</h3>
                  <p>Every three months or so, we’ll let you know how things are going and make sure that we are keeping our savings commitment to you.</p>
